This project currently works with iOS 4.x due to an older version of RestKit that is in use.

Downloads / Cloning:
1) Use the following command so that you get the submodules in one go as well:
    git clone --recursive https://<yourusername>@bitbucket.org/pulkitsinghal/shoppinpal.git
2) If you forget to provide the --recursive flag, you can always download the submodules in a later command using:
    git submodule update --init --recursive

Attributions:
1) RestKit - framework is in use
2) SDWebImage - framework is in use
Make sure to check the LICENSE file as well.

